sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    participant vLLM as vLLM Pod<br/>5557/TCP ZMQ PUB
    participant ZMQ as ZMQ Subscriber<br/>(kvevents)
    participant Pool as KV Events Pool<br/>(sharded workers)
    participant Adapter as Engine Adapter<br/>(vLLM/SGLang)
    participant Index as KV Block Index<br/>(LRU/Ristretto/Redis)
    participant Scheduler as llm-d-inference-scheduler<br/>(embeds library)
    participant Indexer as KV-Cache Indexer<br/>(pkg/kvcache)
    participant TokenPool as Tokenization Pool
    participant UDS as UDS Tokenizer<br/>(gRPC over UDS)
    participant Processor as Token Processor<br/>(FNV-64a hash)
    participant Scorer as KV Block Scorer

    rect rgb(230, 245, 255)
        Note over vLLM,Index: Flow 1: KV-Event Ingestion (Write Path)
        vLLM->>ZMQ: ZMQ PUB 5557/TCP<br/>[topic, seqno, msgpack payload]
        ZMQ->>Pool: Route to worker<br/>(FNV-1a hash of pod ID)
        Pool->>Adapter: Parse event<br/>(msgpack decode)
        Adapter-->>Pool: BlockStored / BlockRemoved<br/>/ AllBlocksCleared
        Pool->>Index: Add/Evict block<br/>(hash → pod location)
    end

    rect rgb(230, 255, 230)
        Note over Scheduler,Scorer: Flow 2: Pod Scoring (Read Path)
        Scheduler->>Indexer: GetPodScores(request)<br/>(in-process or gRPC)
        Indexer->>TokenPool: Tokenize prompt
        TokenPool->>UDS: gRPC Tokenize()<br/>(Unix Domain Socket)
        UDS-->>TokenPool: Token IDs + offsets
        TokenPool-->>Indexer: Tokens
        Indexer->>Processor: Compute block keys<br/>(CBOR + FNV-64a chain)
        Processor-->>Indexer: Block hashes
        Indexer->>Index: Lookup block locations
        Index-->>Indexer: Pod → block mappings
        Indexer->>Scorer: Score(pods, blocks)
        Scorer-->>Indexer: Scored pod list
        Indexer-->>Scheduler: Pod scores<br/>(cache-aware ranking)
    end

    rect rgb(255, 243, 224)
        Note over vLLM,Index: Flow 3: KV-Cache Offloading (Storage Path)
        participant Storage as Shared Storage<br/>(NFS/PVC)
        participant FSMgr as FS Backend Manager
        participant CppEng as C++ storage_offload<br/>(async I/O + GDS)

        vLLM->>FSMgr: OffloadingSpec lookup
        FSMgr->>Storage: stat() check<br/>(POSIX filesystem)
        Storage-->>FSMgr: File exists/not
        vLLM->>CppEng: Transfer blocks
        CppEng->>Storage: Read/Write<br/>(POSIX or GPU-Direct)
        Storage-->>CppEng: KV-cache data
    end

    rect rgb(255, 230, 230)
        Note over vLLM,Index: Flow 4: PVC Eviction
        participant PVC as PVC Mount
        participant Act as Activator<br/>(statvfs polling)
        participant Crawl as N Crawlers<br/>(hex-based LB)
        participant Del as Deleter<br/>(xargs rm)

        Act->>PVC: statvfs() O(1)
        PVC-->>Act: Disk usage %
        Note over Act: Usage > 85% threshold
        Act->>Crawl: Start scanning
        Crawl->>PVC: scandir() by hex range
        PVC-->>Crawl: Eligible files<br/>(atime > 60min)
        Crawl->>Del: Queue files (IPC)
        Del->>PVC: xargs -0 rm -f<br/>(batch delete)
        Note over Act: Stop when < 70%
    end
